reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Stylish and Functional Addition to Our Home Office
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. We recently brought this Huuger Buffet Cabinet with Storage into our home office, and let me tell you, it’s been a purchase we are pleased with. As my husband made the transition to working from home, we found ourselves in need of a storage solution for his professional (and not-so-pretty 😅) book collection. This cabinet turned out to be the perfect match for our needs, and it didn’t break the bank.STYLE THAT WOWS: What truly won us over is the delightful style and very decent quality of this cabinet. It’s not just a functional piece; it’s a lovely addition to our home office. The blend of natural finish and the charming rattan-decorated door surfaces adds a fresh, aesthetically pleasing vibe that seamlessly integrated with our office decor. Plus, those cabinet doors do the trick to hide away those not-so-pretty books. 😂AMPLE STORAGE SPACE: Speaking of storage, this cabinet offered more than enough room to meet our needs. With two rattan doors, an inner shelf, and a spacious top, it can house a variety of items. We even decided to place our printer on top of the shelf. Whether you need a bookshelf, kitchen buffet, storage cabinet, TV console, or even a bar cabinet, this beauty excels in both aesthetics and storage capacity.STURDY AND SECURE: We also appreciate the solid and secure construction of this cabinet. The four sturdy solid wood feet and the included anti-tip kit (which we didn’t opt to install at this time, but it’s great for households with little ones) provide peace of mind when it comes to stability.STRESS-FREE ASSEMBLY: Now, the assembly process might not be our strong suit, but this cabinet’s instructions made it surprisingly straightforward. The instructions were clear, and while they said to allow for 2 hours, my husband got through it in about 1.5 hours, using just a screwdriver.In a nutshell, we can’t recommend this cabinet enough. If you’re on the hunt for a versatile and affordable storage solution that adds style and functionality to your space, look no further.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Looks good, straightforward assembly, a little flimsy
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I had seen that somebody else said it took them six hours to assemble and I was pretty worried. It took me one hour to assemble the first one. I didn’t time the second one so I don’t know.I referred to this as either dollhouse furniture or cheap Airbnb furniture. I would be embarrassed if somebody put something away in this cabinet and saw how cheap it was. But I really like the way it looks. I bought two of them and put them side-by-side as a credenza in my dining room. I needed something cheap and quick and this fit the bill.Based upon the cheap and quick and looks good it gets five stars. But this isn’t something that’s going to stand up to a whole lot of use.The directions were logical and straightforward. And it came with a nice screwdriver!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars So Happy With This Purchase!
reviews.reviewText: I’m usually someone who likes to look, feel the furniture texture/ material before purchasing. I’ve been eying this piece for several months and saw it was on sale recently so took a chance and purchased 3 pieces. The package came well packed, the set up was easy, clear instructions, screwdriver included( a good quality one too!). The wood finish is smooth and well made. The only minus is the doors don’t seem to shut all the way, I’m hoping it will adjust after some use. I’ve always loved the rattan look, so the three pieces together look so neat, natural organic look yet chic. I’m so happy with the purchase and highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Lovely Rattan Cabinet
reviews.reviewText: I bought two of these cabinets and placed them side by side in my entryway.They are ultra stylish and it was easy to put together with 2 people. The first one took a little longer to put together, but once we got the hang of it, we built the second one in a jiffy!Considering the price of these cabinets, they are a great deal for what you get. The storage capacity in these is huge.I was looking for a shoe cabinet and I fit about 12-14 shoes in ONE cabinet alone. Some of the shoes I don't wear often are stacked on top of each other towards the back of the cabinet, and then I have 4 pairs in the very front that are not stacked.We had a little difficulty lining up the doors. They still function perfectly and open smoothly, but if you notice micro details like me, the fact that the doors don't line up perfectly might bother you. That is the only reason I took off one star.Overall, the quality and durability has been good thus far. The cabinet doors open smoothly and they have great storage capacity. I love the natural light wood color as well.
